snippet.title: Former Lovers of Johnny Depp Defend Him Against Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Former Lovers of Johnny Depp Speak On How Kind Johnny Was To Them 
Former lovers of Johnny Depp have spoken up on how extraordinarily kind Johnny had been to them. We are talking about Winona Ryder and Vanessa Paradis, who have come forward in the courts to describe their experience with Johnny Depp. As we all know, Amber Heard’s accusations on Johnny Depp have somewhat tainted his reputation. In such circumstances, the word of his former partners is likely to carry a lot of weight in the ongoing U.S Libel case between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. So, what have they said, and how does it affect Amber Heard’s accusations? Let’s find out.

Here on Film Streak we are all about the latest spill in Hollywood! You can rest assure that we will bring you all the latest celebrity drama and gossip especially concerning you favorite actors! We´ll also make sure to keep you updated on the newest movie updates and releases – so if you are interested in anything that happens in Hollywood, you should make sure to stay tuned!  

And there you have it guys! We hope you enjoyed the video! If you did please consider leaving a like and telling us what you though in the comments!
